@startuml class_calculator_facade

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class CalculatorEngine {
    - _history : list[dict]
    --
    - _record_history(operand1, operator: str, operand2, result) : None
    + get_history() : list[dict]
    .. Basic Arithmetic ..
    + add(a, b) : object
    + subtract(a, b) : object
    + multiply(a, b) : object
    + divide(a, b) : object
    .. Power / Root ..
    + power(base: float, exponent: float) : float
    + square(x: float) : float
    + cube(x: float) : float
    + square_root(x: float) : float
    + cube_root(x: float) : float
    .. Logarithmic ..
    + natural_log(x: float) : float
    + log_base_10(x: float) : float
    .. Factorial ..
    + factorial(n: int) : int
}

note right of CalculatorEngine
  Pure computation engine.
  No UI/IO dependencies.
end note

class Calculator {
    - _engine : CalculatorEngine
    --
    + get_history() : list[dict]
    .. Basic Arithmetic ..
    + add(a, b) : object
    + subtract(a, b) : object
    + multiply(a, b) : object
    + divide(a, b) : object
    .. Power / Root ..
    + power(base: float, exponent: float) : float
    + square(x: float) : float
    + cube(x: float) : float
    + square_root(x: float) : float
    + cube_root(x: float) : float
    .. Logarithmic ..
    + natural_log(x: float) : float
    + log_base_10(x: float) : float
    .. Factorial ..
    + factorial(n: int) : int
}

note right of Calculator
  Facade. All computation
  delegated to CalculatorEngine.
end note

class Logger {
    + get_logger(name) : Logger
}

Calculator *-- CalculatorEngine : delegates to
CalculatorEngine ..> Logger : uses for error logging

@enduml
